                                "literal": {
                                  "string": "The current subterm-path trace, accumulated backwards (head = most-recently-pushed step, corresponding to the deepest point in the descent). At the moment an inference error is constructed, the list is reversed and wrapped into a SubtermPath (root-to-leaf order) and stamped onto the error."}}}]}}}}]},
